response.original_title: Country Legends Live - Nashville Salutes America
response.overview: The Grand Ole Opry House and the Tennessee Performing Arts Center are the settings for this star-studded anthology of performances drawn from a number of musical specials and awards shows. Featuring a who's who of country music, This disc includes the episode "The Best of Nashville Salutes America."
response.title: Country Legends Live - Nashville Salutes America
